//  already exists in the store. This parameter must be one of the following
//  values:
//    CERT_STORE_ADD_NEW
//      Fails if the certificate already exists in the store. LastError
//      is set to CRYPT_E_EXISTS.
//    CERT_STORE_ADD_USE_EXISTING
